04:11.955 --> 04:14.232
Come on, you got to eat something;
what can I get you?

04:14.408 --> 04:16.940
- Beer.
- No, that's what you had for dinner.

04:17.158 --> 04:18.392
Fine.

04:18.575 --> 04:20.582
